      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition car that is about as clean and well-kept as you could hope to find. It runs and drives beautifully, presents extremely well inside and out, and shows only the slightest signs of careful use, if any. The paint, interior, and overall finish are outstanding, and it has the look and feel of a car that has been properly cared for throughout its life. If you\u2019ve been waiting for a truly top-tier example, this is the kind of car that stands out immediately in person.",
