    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an accessible price, this vehicle offers solid value for a buyer who wants an affordable daily driver or practical project. It shows wear consistent with age and prior use, but presents as a straightforward, honest car with plenty of potential for someone who appreciates a smart buy. A great chance to get behind the wheel without overextending your budget.",
