    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels without a lot of fuss? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation and doesn\u2019t mind a vehicle with some age and character. It\u2019s a great fit for a commuter, first-time driver, or anyone who wants something practical at a reasonable price. Priced to reflect its condition, and offered honestly by someone who believes in straightforward deals.",
      "price": 6800.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
