      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with tons of personality, this car has the kind of honest, well-worn character that makes every drive feel like a story in progress. It\u2019s an ideal pick for someone who wants inexpensive wheels today, a hands-on project tomorrow, or simply a vehicle with plenty of life experience and undeniable charm. If you appreciate value, potential, and a car that doesn\u2019t pretend to be anything other than real, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 4900.0,
