      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who wants basic transport, a handy project, or a parts donor with value still left in it. It\u2019s priced to reflect that and could be a great fit for the right buyer who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC. If you\u2019re after something budget-friendly and straightforward, this one is worth a look.",
